'''''Best Chance''''' was a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Shuttle/Legends|shuttle]] in operation during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. In [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]], it ferried a [[Commando/Legends|commando]] team of six [[Noghri/Legends|Noghri]] and three [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]]: [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]], [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]], and [[Ganner Rhysode]], hidden within the decoy [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]] ''[[Lost Hope]]'', from ''[[Ralroost]]'' to the surface of [[Garqi/Legends|Garqi]].

